Thanks to Nintendo for Providing us with Zelda: Breath of the Wild
Subscribe for More GTLive Action! ►► http://bit.ly/1LkSBnz 
Missed Breath of the Wild–Part 3? ►► https://goo.gl/p0uei2
IDIOTS WIN! | Google Autocomplete ►► https://goo.gl/vnWfGr

It's another stream playing BREATH OF THE WILD! What can I say?! I LOVE exploring this Massive World and finding the connections to past Zelda games. It makes me feel a connection to young MatPat. Join us for Part 4 of Breath of the Wild!

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive
